Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.58,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然最后的瞬间只有灵魂会留下
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但灵魂也要消失了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,被赋予了灵魂的容器
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,新的身体 御姿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.27,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我被允许继续作为我自己而生存
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.39,0:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.05,0:00:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我 结城友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明约定过
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.99,0:00:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,却忘记了重要的朋友的事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 才降下了天罚
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡请求神树大人消除我们关于她的记忆
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡果然想法和我不是一个次元的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那种是绝对不允许
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们勇者部夺回了东乡
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那时 我被天神发现了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,作为人 我接触神过多了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我激怒了神
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,神树大人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,地神创造的我的身体受到了诅咒
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 回到第八格？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你又中招了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,第八格 是起点
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.40,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,居然为了因为受伤没法过圣诞和正月的我准备了这个
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木 真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大获成功
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈也谢谢了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我住院的时候 你帮我做了积压的委托吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.64,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不做点什么就冷静不下来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,精神过头了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.77,Top,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,前进四格
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.96,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,突然想从头来过 回到起点
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然歌唱比赛没能取得第一名
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但得到部分铁粉支持 获得一百万日元
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,园子 这是好事还是坏事啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我从秋天就在准备了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不管睡多久…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.37,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你很期待啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.47,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,赌上部长的威严 由我来夺走胜利吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被车撞到 失去所有开心事
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因为心伤休息十回合
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小园 好残酷的游戏啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.27,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人生！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好个大起大落的人生观
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.85,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,园子大人 还有什么吩咐吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经没事了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么告辞
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 还有家政啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我离开家的条件
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,碍事的已经走了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来才是正戏
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.85,0:05:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏呀
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.44,0:05:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我因为某些复杂原因在家里攒了很多东西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么突然
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我去整理物品了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.81,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我调查了很多
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然铺垫很长
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的目的是这个吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者御记？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似有年头了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是乃木家祖传的三百年前的东西哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你读了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正要读
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我知道不太好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想那样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.48,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以第一次想和大家一起读
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,记录我们的战斗 托付给未来的勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,未来的勇者…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木 你找到了什么东西
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在为什么会这样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,必须读这个寻找答案
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也愿意一起读吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小园…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 风前辈
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 大家
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木若叶
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,公元2015年7月
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,绝望从空中降临
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,人类之敌 顶点
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在其不可思议的力量面前
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有对策可言
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.41,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,常识被推翻了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大社
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,知道神话时代流传下来的真实之人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,成为了人们的引导者
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.47,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,人类逃入了灵力守护的防护壁中
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,人们把它称为神树大人的结界
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,斗胆向神树进言…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,2018年 9月
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,与诹访完全失去了联络
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就结果而言 我们把诹访
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当成了守护最重要的四国的诱饵
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,诹访撑了整整三年
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.41,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏如此 得以推进迎击敌人的计划
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.84,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天来临了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,转至灵政策的四国政府
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大社的计划
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.45,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是由寄宿神和精灵之力的少女们组成的战斗部队
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者计划
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请看…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就在刚才 四国政府公布她们是勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 出现啦
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她们正是新的希望
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大社给我们指明了光明前路
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,通过神树大人授予的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她们将消灭顶点
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.16,0:09:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到那些少女会是人类的希望
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大社刚刚发出了新的公告
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道她们的名字了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,根据公告 土居球子
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,伊予岛杏
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,郡千景
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木若叶 重复一遍…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,狂热
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被满怀期待的赞颂
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 不管我们多么拼命
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一切也不可能都是完美的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,生命 是会失去的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,顶点！
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟敢 你竟敢！
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不惜命了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 酒吞童子
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 你的身体会四分五裂的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木 高嶋
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,千景 你那边呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,杂兵已经清除完成了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,伊予岛和土居呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,两人…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有那种事
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.05,0:13:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.16,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道会有牺牲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很危险 快送医院
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.69,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 守护住了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,城市 人…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.45,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.69,0:13:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,两人是为了这个战斗的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拼上性命
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.17,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不能气馁 不能放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不能忘记
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.95,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你还能这么淡定
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那天的绝望和愤怒 我决不会忘记
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要让那些家伙得到报应
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 现在还不能崩溃
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,全身骨折 割伤 烫伤
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,外伤很严重
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是衰弱
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会没法恢复意识
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让勇者死
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奈良县来的高嶋友奈 14岁
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.56,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我走错房间了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是上面的人说今天会来的高嶋友奈吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是友奈酱呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.46,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是友奈酱
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.45,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,球前辈 不能这么称呼初次见面的人哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.86,0:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来明明要结成赌上性命的最强队伍
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这么见外吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不管怎么叫我都可以哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照啦 友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已经直呼姓名了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈是从奈良来的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,球和杏是爱媛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的千景是从高知来的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.59,Top,,0,0,0,,第一次见到四国以外的人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,千景也来自我介绍
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 初次见面 我是…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.81,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.67,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在受到袭击的避难所救了很多人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是很多次
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在新闻上很有名吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 大家都说你是勇者呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦 大名人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定比我们更熟悉战斗呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.48,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是擅长体育
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 我有点精力过剩呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,体育？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是闹着玩
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不理解责任有多重吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈也知道那种事啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,千景真阴暗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 别在意
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,千景总是那样
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,球和杏也很头疼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.90,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,确实…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小郡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,郡？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.08,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 我的名字是…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,乃木
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶这家伙上来就给下马威
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,老师还没来呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.03,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过你的才能 寄宿有天之逆手
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.15,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.70,0:17:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能符合期待
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然会加油的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害呀 若叶
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从你身上一分都拿不到
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才已经死了十次
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那些怪物是不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的战斗很严酷
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱着半吊子心情的话 请你马上离开
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,复仇 我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也背负着呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.46,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这里之前 很多人都没能救到
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说拳头里寄宿着神的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很无力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是很多人救了我 让我站在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来了这里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我比较擅长这个
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是背负一切的英雄
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,正义的英雄啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会气馁 也不会放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很帅的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,帅？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那是电视和漫画里的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.01,0:18:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,憧憬帅气的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那样的勇者比较好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哪边赢了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,两败俱伤
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟很疼的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 请多关照 友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好 来特训吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈真是个不可思议的人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.81,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,球的眼光是不会有错的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是球
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.49,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶 友奈 你们要好好相处啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不许偷懒 你们也开始练习
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶好严格
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不许光看着
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,记好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要为了大家 成为英雄
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成为勇者！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.62,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小球
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.98,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小杏
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道也很疼
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是决定要背负才来到这里的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者 守护人们的战士
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救世界的王牌
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有被选中的我们才能做到
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是因为勇者没能打倒怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以市区才受灾的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者才死了寥寥几个吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是整条街都死了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最初的勇者
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这个到处都被检阅了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎有人整个被抹去了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶是为了留下记录才写的这个吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.35,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说对大赦来说 有些事不能被知道
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.82,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 这个名字是偶然吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也要好好干
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.13,0:23:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目的是打倒敌人 不要搞错使命
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.53,0:23:52.09,Top,,0,0,0,,少啰嗦 少啰嗦 少啰嗦
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.29,Top,,1300,0,0,,有意思吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.09,0:23:52.91,Top,,0,0,0,,快住手 千景
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.91,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,想见…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:53.83,0:23:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.96,0:23:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,知道何谓疼痛吧
